== Availability ==
The Valhalla is present in Terran Conflict's game files, but never spawns. It is seen rarely in (and ''only'' in) war sectors in Albion Prelude.
It can be reverse engineered at the player HQ, taking 5 days and 20 hs to complete. But it can't be built at the Commonwealth player HQ, because its cargo hold is 200K units smaller than the Terran's, and the materials needed won't fit.

== Suggested Roles==
The Valhalla is unique in that it combines the firepower of a heavy [[M2]] such as the [[Tyr]] or [[Osaka]] with the fighter capacity of an {{M1class}} like the [[Argon]] [[Colossus]].  In addition, its ability to project M6 and M8 power means it combines the raw destructive long-range power of an M7M as well.

